snippet.title: Max Time Traveler - From The Future Created By Steve The Producer
snippet.description:
Max Time Traveler - From The Future Created By Steve The Producer
Play with Max, Donata, M.Reck and Steve The Producer and fight the monsters from the future, explore the spaceship and collect coins to survive, use the power-ups and get the best score!

Download https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.maxtimetraveler.fromfuture&hl=en_US&gl=US
